{
  "stem": "11611.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very stylish uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I liked them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Never wore them much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Up till the end of that year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, let's see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's right, up-- up to about December.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then my group-- by my group-- I said there were 40 or 50 people who went into the Marine Corps. 10 or 12-- I think 12-- were then earmarked for one of the new Marine divisions that were being formed, in this case, the 4th Marine Division.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the complement for the 4th Marine Division, which was just being put together, consisted of a bunch of odd units here and there in the Marine Corps being reformulated in a new organization.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the division itself was just being put together, and to put us in some kind of standby status, we were then shipped, I think 12 of us, to an Army camp in Japanese language located near Minneapolis-- Camp Savage, Minnesota.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Attended more Japanese classes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was an interesting camp, because it had Army people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It also had Canadian army people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then it had 12 Marines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as far as I know, we were the only Marines in the city of Minneapolis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was married, so that put me under certain handicaps, but the rest of my colleagues had a damn good times.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When was I married?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "June of 1942.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was even before that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Chicago.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Elsie Spira, S-P-I-R-A.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She went through school with me in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I think two, three months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were put on ice until the end of the year, when we joined the division in California.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The 4th Division was formed sometime in the fall of '43.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Camp Pendleton, I think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's near Oceanside, California, between San Diego and Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
